{
  "stem": "1895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was what we talked about, and that was the state, that I remember, of mind of my father's generation and my generation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My generation began to look towards Palestine as the redeeming-- the place of redemption, the place to go to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew that under no circumstances can we continue to live in this godforsaken place where everybody hated us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's generation was somewhat different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they were more practical, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that the world is not an oyster, and nobody's exactly waiting for Jews, to welcome them with open arms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he knew from practical experience that the little that we have needs to be preserved and cherished.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've thought about that often.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really can't blame him, because I'm now in a situation where I can identify with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was 52 when he perished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at 52, you think not in terms of a 15- or 16-year-old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You think in terms of someone who has the sole responsibilities to sustain a family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on that basis, I cannot blame him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had his connections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had his past.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had his present.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He has the future right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He knew how to make the most of the terrible situation that we were in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he also knew that he would always manage to sustain the family where he was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can I blame him for not leaving this place and going into a world that was hostile to Jews anyway, and starting from scratch at that age?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't blame him for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you remember any family vacations growing up?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
